{"title_page": "Rinkaku (song)", "text_new": "{{multiple issues|{{refimprove|date=September 2017}}{{third-party|date=September 2017}}}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = Rinkaku\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| album      = [[Arche (album)|Arche]]\n| B-side     = Kiri to Mayu\n| released   = December 19, 2012\n| format     =\n| recorded   =\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{hlist|[[Art rock]]|[[progressive metal]]}}\n| length     =\n| label      = [[Firewall Div.]]\n| composer   =\n| lyricist   =\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = [[Different Sense]]\n| prev_year  = 2011\n| next_title = Sustain the Untruth\n| next_year  = 2014\n}}\n\n'''\"Rinkaku\"''' is the 28th [[single (music)|single]] by [[Japanese rock]] band [[Dir en Grey]], released on December 19, 2012. Its highest ranking reached fourth place on the weekly [[Oricon]] chart.<ref name=\"oricon\">{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/music/release/d/988336/1/|title= Oricon artists archive|accessdate=2013-02-26|language=ja}}</ref> \nThe original cover art is created by vocalist [[Kyo (musician)|Kyo]], which was shown at various venues in Japan after release of the single.<ref>{{cite web\n| title      = Single info, Dir En Grey \n| work       = direngrey.co.jp\n| url        = http://www.direngrey.co.jp/yoyaku.html#art\n| accessdate = 2013-04-18\n|language=ja}}\n</ref> Rinkaku was released in three editions (regular, limited, and an order-only deluxe edition).\n\n==Tracks==\n{{Tracklist\n| all_lyrics      = [[Kyo (musician)|Kyo]]\n| title1          = Rinkaku\n| note1           = {{Nihongo2|\u8f2a\u90ed; \"Contours\"}}\n| length1         = 5:42\n| title2          = Kiri to Mayu\n| note2           = {{Nihongo2|\u9727\u3068\u7e6d; \"Fog and Cocoon\"}}\n| length2         = 4:13\n| music2          = [[Kaoru (musician)|Kaoru]]\n| title3          = Rinkaku Eternal Slumber Mix (Remixed by [[Akira Yamaoka]])\n| length3         = 5:37\n| music3          = \n| note3           = {{Nihongo2|\u8f2a\u90ed Eternal Slumber Mix (Remixed by Akira Yamaoka); \"Contours Eternal Slumber Mix (Remixed by Akira Yamaoka)\"}}\n}}\n\n===Limited Edition DVD===\n{{Track listing\n| all_lyrics      =\n| title1          = Rinkaku\n| note1           = Scenes from Recording\n| music1          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n}}\n\n===Deluxe Edition DVD===\n{{Track listing\n| title1          = Amon\n| note1           = \n| music1          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title2          = Lotus\n| note2           = \n| music2          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title3          = Obscure\n| note3           = \n| music3          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title4          = Ruten no T\u014d\n| note4           = {{Nihongo2|\u6d41\u8ee2\u306e\u5854; \"Tower of Vicissitudes\"}}\n| music4          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title5          = Akatsuki\n| note5           = {{Nihongo2|\u6681; \"Dawn\"}}\n| music5          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title6          = Hageshisa to, Kono Mune no Naka de Karamitsuita Shakunetsu no Yami\n| note6           = {{Nihongo2|\u6fc0\u3057\u3055\u3068\u3001\u3053\u306e\u80f8\u306e\u4e2d\u3067\u7d61\u307f\u4ed8\u3044\u305f\u707c\u71b1\u306e\u95c7; \"The Violence and the Darkness of the Burning Heat Entwines In My Heart\"}}\n| music6          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title7          = The Blossoming Beelzebub\n| note7           = \n| music7          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title8          = Mazohyst of Decadence\n| note8           = \n| music8          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title9          = Tsumi to Batsu\n| note9           = {{Nihongo2|\u871c\u3068\u553e; \"Crime and Punishment / Honey and Saliva\"}}\n| music9          = [[Dir En Grey]]\n| title10         = 'Yokus\u014d ni Dreambox' Aruiwa Seijuku no Rinen to Tsumetai Ame\n| note10          = {{Nihongo2|\u300c\u6b32\u5de3\u306bDREAMBOX\u300d\u3042\u308b\u3044\u306f\u6210\u719f\u306e\u7406\u5ff5\u3068\u51b7\u305f\u3044\u96e8; \"'Nesting Within the Dreambox', or Cold Rain and the Philosophy of the Mature\"}}\n| music10      