ign=right}}\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Interchange\n| align=\"center\" |[[Christyl Stowers]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |[[Kyara Nean]] {{leagueicon|South Sydney|size=16|align=right}}\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Interchange\n| align=\"center\" |Kathleen (Wharton) Keremete\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |[[Regan Hart]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Interchange\n| align=\"center\" |Charlette (Harata) Butler\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |[[Tommaya Kelly Sines]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Interchange\n| align=\"center\" |[[Kerehitina Matua]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |[[Layna Nona Busch]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Interchange\n| align=\"center\" |[[Acacia Claridge-Te Iwimate]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |[[Dean Widders]]\n| align=\"center\" |Coach\n| align=\"center\" |[[Rusty Matua]]\n|}\n\n== Result ==\n{{rugbyleaguebox|bg=#f1f5fc|date=15 February 2019|time=|team1=[[Indigenous All Stars (rugby league)|Indigenous Women's All Stars]]|score=4 &ndash; 8|report=|team2={{flagicon|New Zealand M\u0101ori}} [[New Zealand Maori rugby league team|Maori Women's All Stars]]|points1='''Tries:'''<br/>Shakiah Tungai (31') '''1'''|points2='''Tries:'''<br/>Tyler Birch (10') '''1'''<br/>[[Krystal Rota]] (54') '''1'''|stadium=[[AAMI Park]]|referees=|attendance=}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{2019 in rugby league}}\n\n[[Category:2019 NRL season|All Stars Match]]\n[[Category:NRL All Stars match]]\n[[Category:Sports competitions in Melbourne]]\n[[Category:Rugby league in Victoria (Australia)]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox rugby league football match (quarters)|year=2019|title=All Stars match|image=|imagesize=150px|alt=|home=Indigenous All Stars|away=M\u0101ori All Stars|home_abbr=IND|away_abbr=MAO|home_quarter1=10|home_quarter2=10|home_quarter3=4|home_quarter4=10|home_total=34|away_quarter1=6|away_quarter2=4|away_quarter3=4|away_quarter4=0|away_total=14|date=15 February 2019|stadium=[[Melbourne Rectangular Stadium|AAMI Park]]|location=[[Melbourne]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]]|MoM_title=[[Preston Campbell]] Medal|MoM=[[Tyrone Roberts]]|anthem_title=|anthem=|referee=Grant Atkins|referee2=Gavin Badger|attendance=18,802|network=|commentators=Mat Thompson|commentators2=[[Phil Gould]]|commentators3=[[Andrew Johns]]|commentators4=|tournaments=[[All Stars match]]|last=[[2017 All Stars match|2017]]|next=[[2020 All Stars match|2020]]}}The '''2019 All Stars match''' was the eighth annual representative exhibition [[All Stars match]] of [[Rugby league in Australia|Australian rugby league]]. The match was played between the [[Indigenous All Stars (rugby league)|Indigenous All Stars]] and the [[New Zealand M\u0101ori rugby league team|M\u0101ori All Stars]] and for the first time, the match was played in [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]]'s [[Melbourne Rectangular Stadium|AAMI Park]]. The match was held on the 15 February 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sportingnews.com/au/league/news/nrl-announce-new-all-stars-concept-indigenous-new-zealand-maori-2019-pre-season-josh-addo-carr-jesse-bromwich/1perz3wa9qkp01rbyp50rv50xo|title=NRL announce new All-Stars concept to kick-off 2019 NRL season|website=www.sportingnews.com|language=en-AU|access-date=2018-11-04}}</ref>\n\n== Teams ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: 1em auto 1em auto\"\n!  align=\"centre\" style=\"width:170px; border:3px solid gold; background:black; color:white\"|INDIGENOUS<br>ALL STARS\n! align=\"center\" width=\"100\" style=\"background: #eeeeee; color: black\" |Position\n!  align=\"centre\" style=\"width:170px; border:3px solid darkgreen; background:white; color:darkgreen\"|M\u0100ORI<br>ALL STARS\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Alex Johnston (rugby league)|Alex Johnston]]<sup>2</sup> {{leagueicon|South Sydney|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Fullback\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Auckland|size=16|align=left}} [[Peta Hiku]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Blake Ferguson]] {{leagueicon|Parramatta|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Wing\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|South Sydney|size=16|align=left}} [[Dane Gagai]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Latrell Mitchell]] {{leagueicon|Eastern Suburbs|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Centre\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Wests Tigers|size=16|align=left}} [[Esan Marsters]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[James Roberts (rugby league)|James Roberts]] {{leagueicon|Brisbane|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Centre\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Penrith|size=16|align=left}} [[Dean Whare]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Josh Addo-Carr]] {{leagueicon|Melbourne|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Wing\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|North Queensland|size=16|align=left}} [[Jordan Kahu]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Cody Walker (rugby league)|Cody Walker]] (c) {{leagueicon|South Sydney|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Five-eighth\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Newcastle|size=16|align=left}} [[Kalyn Ponga]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Tyrone Roberts]] {{leagueicon|Gold Coast Titans|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Halfback\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Melbourne|size=16|align=left}} [[Jahrome Hughes]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Andrew Fifita]] {{leagueicon|Cronulla|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Prop\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Melbourne|size=16|align=left}} [[Jesse Bromwich]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Nathan Peats]] {{leagueicon|Gold Coast Titans|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background: #eeeeee\" |Hooker\n|align=\"center\"|{{leagueicon|Melbourne|size=16|align=left}} [[Brandon Smith (rugby league)|Brandon Smith]]\n|-\n|align=\"center\"|[[Leilani Latu]]<sup>1</sup> {{leagueicon|Gold Coast Titans|size=16|align=right}}\n|align=\"ce